					<li class="book-item active"><a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20210918093740/http://catholicbible.online/vulgate/OT/1Mcc">Machabæorum I</a></li>
					<li class="book-item"><a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20210918093740/http://catholicbible.online/vulgate/OT/2Mcc">Machabæorum II</a></li>
			</ul>
</div>
	<div class="main">
		<div class="main-content">
			<div class="book-header">
				<div class="vers-view-type">
